OL,7,FThe UK Government should not ramp up
OL,8,Fthe decline of Scotland's oil and gas
OL,9,Findustry, a report has urged, after it
OL,10,Ffound jobs created in clean energy are
OL,11,Ffailing to make up for losses in the
OL,12,FNorth Sea.
OL,14,FThe report by the House of Commons
OL,15,FScottish Affairs Committee warned the
OL,16,Fsector is now at a "critical juncture"
OL,17,Fas the nation moves away from fossil
OL,18,Ffuels and towards renewable energy.
