OL,3,CUK Government must not ramp up decline
OL,4,Cof Scottish oil and gas sector, MPs
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FThe report, the first part of its
OL,8,Finquiry into GB Energy and the net
OL,9,Fzero transition, warned that until
OL,10,Fclean energy jobs can be created at
OL,11,Fthe scale needed to match current
OL,12,Ffossil fuel job losses, the UK
OL,13,FGovernment "should avoid accelerating
OL,14,Fthe decline of North Sea oil and gas
OL,15,Fproduction".
OL,17,FMPs called on the UK Government to set
OL,18,Fout urgently how it will address the
OL,19,Femployment gap.
