OL,3,CUK Government must not ramp up decline
OL,4,Cof Scottish oil and gas sector, MPs
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FThe report said as fossil fuels will
OL,8,Fcontinue to form part of the UK's
OL,9,Fenergy mix for decades, there are
OL,10,F"compelling arguments" for the
OL,11,F"gradient of UK production decline to
OL,12,Fbe eased, to meet as much energy
OL,13,Fdemand as possible from domestic
OL,14,Fsources".
OL,16,FThe committee added: "Doing so will
OL,17,Fmean Scotland retains highly skilled
OL,18,Fsupply chain workers, rather than
OL,19,Fbeing lost to overseas markets, which
OL,20,Fare vital for the growth of clean
OL,21,Fenergy sectors."
