OL,8,Fchairwoman of the Scottish Affairs
OL,9,FCommittee, said: "Today's report
OL,10,Foutlines our concerns that jobs from
OL,11,Fthe clean energy industry are simply
OL,12,Fnot being created fast enough, or on
OL,13,Fthe scale needed, to match the
OL,14,Fmounting job losses from the oil and
OL,15,Fgas sector.
